@calculator @addition
Feature: Calculator Functionality

  Background:
    Given a calculator is turned on

  @smoke
  Scenario: Add two numbers
    # This is a comment providing additional information about the scenario
    Given the user enters the number 5 into the calculator
    And the user enters the number 7 into the calculator
    When the user adds the numbers
    Then the result should be 12 on the screen

  @subtraction
  Scenario: Subtract two numbers
    # Another comment for clarification
    Given the user enters the number 10 into the calculator
    And the user enters the number 4 into the calculator
    When the user subtracts the numbers
    Then the result should be 6 on the screen
